#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.koko.appdata.xml:72
msgid ""
"This release modernizes the settings page, updates the style of the album "
"page and adds a confirmation dialog before discarding image edits. This also "
"fixes the full screen and slideshow mode."
msgstr ""
"Iste version modernisa le pagina de preferentias, actualisa le stilo del "
"pagina de album e adde un dialogo de confirmation ante annullar "
"modificationes de imagine. Isto anque corrige le modo de schermo plen e de "
"presentation a diapositiva. "

